skall man estraktera iso i c-xbox tool ?

1. Unpack rar to .ISO
2. Unpack ISO (using QWix or cxbox-tool) to folder structure.
3. Remove default.bak in root. Only default.xbe remains.
4. Repack to ISO (using same tool as in step 2)
5. Burn new ISO on DVD5 format.
6. Works fine!
